snippet.title: Puzzling Places: Cherry Blossom (Collaboration with Walkabout Mini Golf)
snippet.description:
Special collaboration with Walkabout Mini Golf—A free DLC puzzle featuring Cherry Blossom, a fan-favorite course from Walkabout Mini Golf is available to download in Puzzling Places!

Piece together Cherry Blossom while admiring all the little, intricate details of the puzzle. Listen to the incredible sound design that slowly builds as you progress through the regions. Find the little hidden easter egg characters sprinkled throughout the scene! 

Full details: https://puzzlingplaces.ghost.io/cherry-blossom/
